            "text": "Here are some options for professional facial treatments in Katy, TX, based on the search results:\n\n**Med Spas & Clinics:**\n\n*   **Anita's Skin Care Clinic:** This clinic offers customized facials, threading, dermaplaning, chemical peels, and waxing services. Anita takes a holistic approach, tailoring treatments to address individual skin concerns. They specialize in holistic skincare and beauty therapy treatments.\n*   **SkinSpirit Katy:** This medical spa offers custom facials, signature facials, and other aesthetic treatments like Botox, fillers, microneedling, and chemical peels. They focus on tailoring each treatment to your skin's needs.\n*   **Luminous MediSpa Katy:** They offer a range of services from facials and skin rejuvenation to injectables and laser treatments.\n*   **Face to Face Spa:** This beauty med spa offers high-quality treatments supported by medical guidance in a calm and welcoming setting. Services include classic facials and Hydrafacials. They also have a special offer for first-time clients: a 60-minute Premium Medi-Facial with a choice of chemical peel or microdermabrasion for $149.\n*   **Katy Med Tech Spa:** They offer personalized treatments and focus on customer service. First-time customers can get an Ageless Signature Facial or a luxurious Body Treatment for $59.99.\n*   **LUXE Medical Aesthetics:** This med spa combines cutting-edge techniques and professional care with high-quality products. They offer signature facials.\n\n**Day Spas:**\n\n*   **Spavia Cinco Ranch:** This day spa offers massage, facials, body treatments and waxing in a luxury setting.\n*   **Hand & Stone Katy:** They provide professional spa services at affordable prices, including various facials. Introductory classic facials are offered for $79.95 for non-members.\n\n**Other Options:**\n\n*   **The Only Facial:** They specialize in one signature facial, customizing the steps to each individual's skin type and concerns. They also offer a Teen Facial.\n*   **Hibiscus Aesthetics & Wellness:** They offer Hydrafacial, Acne Facial, Glow Facial, Chemical Peel and SkinPen Microneedling.\n*   **Divinity Spa:** They offer customized facial treatments using techniques like radiofrequency, ultrasound, and illuminator.\n\n**Deals:**\n\n*   **Groupon:** Check Groupon for deals on facials in and near Katy, TX.\n\nIt's recommended to check recent reviews and compare services and pricing before making a decision.\n"
          }
        ],
